1. The player starts with an empty 
square table that shows the "minefield"

2. Touch on a square in the table...

3. If a mine box is sure, the player marks 
with a flag (press to mark or unmark flag)

4. When the 8 neighboring cells in some 
have enough mines and there are still 
others, those cells do not have mines

5. The game ends with a win for players 
if all mines-free cells are opened
